quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  56,51,"Refti onon fennoo…ìe ummital majju…ìe laawol poocingol ko √±aamoo…ìe √±ande darnga e …ìesnaa…óe lekki Jaqquum ko kiin …ìuri bonde e so…ìde …ìesnaa…óe."
  56,52,"56:51"
  56,53,"Leggal ngal hebbiiroyton dim…óe mun haa…óu…óe, deedi mon yeewu…ói."
  56,54,"Surkoron ngal ndiyam wul…óam haa fati."
  56,55,"On …óu…ó…óiniroyay yarugol e maggal, wano ngelooba …óu…ó…óinirta yarugol si √±awii."
  56,56,"Ko on √±aametee mettu…óo e ndiyam haa…óu…óo, woni ko …ìe ja…ì…ìortee √±alnde njo…ìdi kuu…óe mon."
  56,57,"Ko Menen tagi on, onon yo fennu…ìe ummital, hari on woodaaka. Ko ha…ói on goonginnde wonnde Men wuurnitay on si on maayii?"
  56,58,"Onon …ìee yim…ìe, on yi'ii maniiyu mo rufoton on e rennga rew…ìe …ìen?"
  56,59,"Ko onon tagata on maniiyu? Kaa ko Menen woni tagoo…ìe mo?"
  56,60,"Ko Menen woni ko hoddiri maayde nden hakkunde mon; gooto kala e lajal, aditotaako wattintaako. Men wonaali ronkitee…ìe."
  56,61,"E wattitugol honoo…ìe mon e tagudu e mbaadi mon, Men fu…ó…óira on e ko on anndaano e tagudu e mbaadi."
  56,62,"Gom…óii hi…óon anndi no Men tagiri on non ka aranun. E on taskotaako anndon wonnde tagu…óo On aranun …óum, hino hattani immintingol on si on maayii?"
  56,63,"On yi'ii gabbe …óe sankoton …óen ka leydi?"
  56,64,"Ko onon fu…óinta …óen gabbe? Kaa ko Menen?"
  56,65,"Si Men haajuno wa…óugol ndun remuru foron, ko pellet, Men wattayno mo …óum, fewndo ka …ìadini ∆¥o∆¥ugol. Wattinon …ìaawo …óum, hi…óon ≈ãal…óa e ko he…ìu ngu."
  56,66,"Wi'on : Menen ko men leptiraa…ìe hayrugol ko men nafqi kon."
  56,67,"Wurin ko men haaa…ìe arsike."
  56,68,"On yi'ii ndiyam …óam yaroton …óam si on …óom…óaama?"
  56,69,"E ko onon saa∆¥iniri …óam ka kammu? Kaa ko Menen saa∆¥ini …óam?"
  56,70,"Si Men haajuno wa…óugol …óam ndiyam …óuu…óu…óam lam…óam, hara …óam nafataa yarugol wanaa yarnirgol, ko pellet, Men wa…óayno …óum. Ko ha…ói on yettugol Allah e ko O jippiniri yurmeende Makko nden kon, ndiyam wel…óam?"
  56,71,"On yi'ii yiite nge hu…ì…ìirton haajuuji mon …óin?"
  56,72,"E ko onon tagi le…ó…óe hu…ì…ìirtee…óe ngen yiite? Kaa ko Menen tagiri …óe yurmegol on?"
  56,73,"Men wa…óir ngee yiite ko waajitoron Yiite laakara ngen, e nafitor nge setotoo…ìe mon."
  56,74,"Subbunhinor an Nulaa…óo, Joomi maa, Mawnu…óo e ko O hanndaa e mun."
  56,75,"Allah woondirii nokkuuli koode …óen."
  56,76,"Ko pellet, woondirgol mutir…óe …óee koode, ko maw…óum, si …óon anndunoo. Tawde maandeeji e tasakuyeeji no ton ko lannataa."